description:
Card #18 - Base Points:9

Summoned byThe Two Wizards of the Cryptoverse, an army of Gogos were born. Each unique. Each with a particular mission.  Delivered one by one by  The Keeper of the Traits. #4958 ready.

Perks when buying this card:

1) All buyers participate in the raffle for the 1/1 Artwork
2) Every copy you buy is an extra chance to win
***************************************************************************
3) The 10 people who buy the most amount of copies of this card will receive Card #19
***************************************************************************
4) The 1/1 artwork of that card will be raffled among those 10 people
5) This edition will have future utility! Extra copies will be useful to exchange for another card.
6) Combinable Cards with each other in the Cards Showdown. Adds 2 bonus points


- This will be the last drop prior to the Cards Tournament, for which you'll need at least 4 different cards to participate
